reviewText: This dvd features 4 episodes from the short "Wish Kid" tv series which starred the voice of a young Macaulay Culkin. The episodes featured are: "Gross encounters", "Lotto trouble", "A matter of principal", and "Top gun, will travel". If you're a fan of Mack and "Home Alone" style stories, and of '90s Saturday morning cartoons, you'll love it!
